## About TTİ İZMİR

TTİ İZMİR (International Tourism Trade Fair and Congress) is Turkey's largest tourism platform, bringing together travel industry professionals for the 19th edition. This comprehensive event combines exhibition, B2B meetings, and congress sessions.

## Event Components

Destination Exhibitions | Hotel Presentations | Tour Operators | Travel Technology | MICE Services | Tourism Congress

## Event Highlights

**400+ Exhibitors** and **25,000+ Visitors** including travel agencies, tour operators, hotels, and tourism boards make TTİ İZMİR Turkey's premier tourism industry event.

## Why Attend

Access Turkey's tourism market, discover new destinations and products, network with travel professionals, and participate in industry congress sessions addressing tourism trends.
